title: Miss Montreal
text:
Miss Montreal
We can use your help. Send us and email if you wish to become a video moderator.
The song I Am Hunter by Miss Montreal has been listed for 7 weeks on the Dutch Top 40. It entered the chart on position 35 on week 16/2012, it's last appearance was on week 22/2012. It peaked on number 28, where it stayed for 1 week. Below you'll find the exact numbers and statistics.
